|           PaymentStatus              |
---------------------------------------
| PENDING                              |
| SUCCESS                              |
| FAILED                               |
| CANCELLED                            |
---------------------------------------


2. Relationships in class diagram
Total 6 main types of relationships are:
	association, aggregation, composition, inheritance, implementation and dependency

	1. Association : USES/KNOWS relationship
		ClassA  ─────────  ClassB

	2. Aggregation : HAS-A (weak relationship)
		Whole  ◇────────  Part
		Team  ◇────────  Player

	3. Composition : HAS-A (strong relationship)
		Whole  ◆────────  Part
		House  ◆────────  Room

	4. Inheritance : IS-A
		Child  ─────────▷  Parent
		Dog  ─────────▷  Animal

	5. Interface Implementation (Realization) : CAN-DO
		Class  - - - - ▷  Interface
		Bird  - - - - ▷  Flyable

	6. Dependency - USES TEMPORARILY
		ClassA  - - - - - >  ClassB
		OrderService  - - - - >  PaymentService

