Question : how will you get all the books borrowed by a user
Answer : 
	Keep list of books in User class. WRONG : as this will break single source of truth concept Book.borrowedBy and User.booksBorrowed list will convey same thing
	Library has access of all books and book store data borrowedBy. loop through all book and get data. And for that, introduce a method in Library as + getBooksBorrowedBy(int userId) : List<Book>